Q: If i have workload with memory centric, what ec2 instance type must i choose ?
A: EC2 Instance typr R


Q: I have two instances, deployed in same region and same availability zone, what else should  i do to reduce latency between this instance ?
A: Connect via VPC Peering


Q: If you have two VPC, how to connect them ?
A: Membuat VPC Peering


Q: How to make private subnet on VPC can access the internet ? explain the steps  in details
A: Membuat Transit Gateway


